{
  "text": "Previous research has indicated a direct relationship was found between customers' future intention to purchase, loyalty, brand image, brand awareness, attitude toward the brand [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Research directions could be paid more attention to relevant factors and investigate the relationships among each of the variables. Moreover, future research could also examine differences of customer's time perception and conformity between groups of first-time and returning customers, and investigate whether the conformity behavior and time perception would be affected by consumption experience and word of mouth communication.",
  "correct_citation": {
